{
  "stem": "21582.7",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And what we ate was, I remember [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the only people who really helped us was one Jew would help another one.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And if we would know that there was a field where there were potatoes, we would dug-- dig potatoes if we could find it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But it was-- it was-- it was a tremendous starvation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We begged.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we-- and we made our way to Kielce.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And in Kielce, we never found the cousins.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They did not survive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I remember when we approached, when we entered in Kielce, dusk was falling.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And we were anxious to find shelter.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we were chased by-- by taunting Poles who were throwing [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] rocks and things at us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And a door opened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And an old woman who looked like a witch came out, was wearing this big skirt, and-- and a black babushka, toothless.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "She opened the door.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And she said to all of us, come in, come in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And she gave us shelter, which was a very, very daring thing to do.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Because, you know, that her neighbors will take it out on her.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "She was very, very poor.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "She just had this one room and the stove.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "She had a little borscht that she shared with us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And-- and we had shelter and warmth.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And it was-- it's one person that I wish that I had been able or made an effort to find her, because she was very special.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was-- it was a very, very long process.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Eventually, we did find our way to our cousins.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in Kielce, the shelter that we found was-- there were-- there was one Jewish-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a few Jewish men, Russian soldiers.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One was a tailor.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
